content: Hi! April here from Colorado. I did the texting training earlier this week and submitted the quiz and the form. I don't see that I've been added to the texting channel. I'd love to get started reaching voters through texting!
Hi mods I can check on this.
It looks like one of our greeters should of sent you a direct message on 8/28. Do you see that message?
I can direct message you it if you haven't done it.

Hi <@681347833303269377> you can find direct messages in the upper-left corner of your screen. There is a game-controller icon (Discord logo) and you will see a red dot. Click on the icon and the direct message panel will open.
